    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for practical transportation. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading, and a few small dings consistent with regular use over the years. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining, though the cabin remains functional and smoke-free. While it isn't a showroom piece, it has been maintained to stay roadworthy and offers a budget-friendly option for those who prioritize utility over aesthetics.",
